sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Controller
    participant UC as Use-Case (create/update)
    participant V as validateRowPayload
    participant P as RowPasswordService
    participant SE as ScriptExecutionService (VM)
    participant R as RowRepository (Mongoose)
    participant H as Hook pre/post save (model-builder)
    participant N as Notification/Mention Services

    C->>UC: execute(payload)
    UC->>V: valida tipos/required/formato
    V-->>UC: errors | null
    alt errors
        UC-->>C: Left 400 INVALID_PAYLOAD_FORMAT
    end
    UC->>P: hash campos PASSWORD
    UC->>SE: execute beforeSave (moment=antes_salvar) [explicito no use-case]
    SE-->>UC: ExecutionResult {success, logs, error}
    note over UC,SE: erro de script NAO bloqueia o save no use-case (apenas loga)
    UC->>R: create/update na collection dinamica
    R->>H: pre('save') -> executeScript beforeSave [2a execucao]
    note over H: pre-save: erro de script LANCA e ABORTA o save
    R->>H: post('save') -> executeScript afterSave (moment=depois_salvar)
    note over H: post-save: afterSave NAO bloqueante (so console.error)
    R-->>UC: row persistido
    UC->>N: notifyNewMembers (KANBAN/CALENDAR) / notifyNewMentions (KANBAN)
    UC->>P: mask campos PASSWORD
    UC-->>C: Right(row)
